Project: HabitFlow

Stack:
- Next.js App Router
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- Tailwind + shadcn/ui
- Chart.js

Rules:
- Use functional React components
- Use Tailwind for styling
- Use shadcn components
- Use API routes for backend
- Use Mongoose models for DB
- Habit logs must be stored per date
- Do not store streak directly; calculate it
- Write clean, modular code
- Use async/await